Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.34,other,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\an1\blur4\3c&H0A0A0A&\3a&H63&\pos(424,886)}海胆水芹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易打扮得这么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想去喝一杯再回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这附近哪里有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时间还这么热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁板烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再喝一杯还得是啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}才没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:56.70,other,,0,0,0,,{\u1\fn华文行楷\c&H4B55B8&\bord2\blur2\fs50\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&}水芹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:56.70,other,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.5\blur2\3c&H0A0A0A&\3a&H00&}是一种有特殊辣味的蔬菜\N一般为肉类做配菜。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海胆水芹 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海胆水芹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是悄然成为广岛名点的食物呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我海胆水芹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这到底是什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄油？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量的水芹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和黄油炒在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海胆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超好吃的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是海胆水芹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不和法棍一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚好水芹的苦味消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海胆比生吃的时候更有海胆的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为是少有的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这简直是脑子里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美味拼图般的完美结合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是第一次吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却好像早就知道这美味一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这是海胆奢侈的吃法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却只起着平民小菜一样的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}海胆水芹真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.09,other,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur4\pos(429,162)\fad(0,312)}明明今天才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵 就是说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 价格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.72,other,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H8471B2&\bord0\frz352.2\pos(341,194)}海胆水芹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不能经常点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次也把这个告诉大家吧
